// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2996 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c2576aa0-a079-58db-a72b-3d9cf082ab36

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
